gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 120, 76ers 109
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the 76ers, 120-109. Lauri Markkanen led the way for the Jazz with 33 points (5-9 3PM) and 13 rebounds, with Collin Sexton adding 22 points and 10 assists in the victory. Kelly Oubre Jr. tallied 24 points, four rebounds, and four assists for the 76ers in the defeat. The Jazz improve to 17-20 in the regular season, while the 76ers fall to 23-12.
